d (`stats/org.apache.groovy/groovy-yaml/4.0.24/execution-metrics.json` shows `generated_loc: 0` and `artifacts.test_file: None`).\n\nNext steps:\n- Replace the generated Groovy test with a hand-written library-specific test that avoids Groovy test-source invokedynamic/bootstrap issues under native image.\n- Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.groovy:groovy-yaml:4.0.24` and confirm both JVM and native phases execute real tests instead of `NO-SOURCE` / `SKIPPED`.\n- Revisit metadata only after the replacement test is stable; the recorded failures do not show a clear remaining `Missing*RegistrationError`."}}
